---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';


---

<Layout title="Bay of Islands Holiday Home Support">

<div style="line-height: 1.6;">


  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem) 1rem;
">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
  Reliable Holiday Home Support<br />
  in the Bay of Islands
</h1>


    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1.2rem; max-width: 720px;">
      I provide local oversight, changeover checks, and practical on-the-ground support
      for holiday home owners who can’t always be here themselves.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 720px;">
      This is not full property management — it’s a calm, reliable layer of support
      that helps prevent small issues becoming expensive or stressful ones.
    </p>


<p style="margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 720px; font-weight: 600;">
  Currently accepting <span style="white-space: nowrap;">2–3</span> new properties.
</p>


  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT’S FOR -->
  <section class="light-section" style="padding: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem) 1rem;">

    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2>Who this is for</h2>

      <ul style="margin-top:1rem;">
        <li>You own a holiday home in the Bay of Islands</li>
        <li>You live elsewhere or aren’t always nearby</li>
        <li>You want someone local keeping an eye on things</li>
        <li>You value clear boundaries, communication, and reliability</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">
        I work with a limited number of properties so I can be consistent, responsive,
        and familiar with each home.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem) 1rem;
">
    <h2>Services</h2>

    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      Services are structured as monthly plans with a set number of visits.
      This keeps things fair, predictable, and avoids over- or under-servicing.
    </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
  <h3>Essential Oversight</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>$280 per month</strong><br />
    Up to 6 service visits per month for low-use homes.
  </p>
</div>

<div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
  <h3>Active Hosting Support</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>$420 per month</strong><br />
    Up to 12 service visits per month for regularly booked properties.
  </p>
</div>

<div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
  <h3>High-Turnover Care</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>$650 per month</strong><br />
    Up to 20 service visits per month for busy or premium homes.
  </p>
</div>


    <p style="margin-top:1rem;">
      Additional visits are charged per use. Scope is clear and agreed upfront.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST -->
  <section class="light-section" style="padding: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem) 1rem;">

    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2>How I work</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Scheduled service days — no constant interruptions</li>
        <li>Clear communication and photo reporting</li>
        <li>Issues flagged early, not after guests arrive</li>
        <li>Professional boundaries (no scope creep)</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">
        My role is to support your property — not to replace cleaners, trades,
        or full management services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ENQUIRY -->
  <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem) 1rem;
">
    <h2>Enquire</h2>

    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      If you’re looking for a local, reliable point of contact for your holiday home,
      you’re welcome to get in touch below.
    </p>

    <form
      name="holiday-home-enquiry"
      method="POST"
      data-netlify="true"
      netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
    >
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="holiday-home-enquiry" />
      <p hidden>
        <label>Don’t fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
      </p>

      <p>
        <label>
          Name<br />
          <input type="text" name="name" required />
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>
        <label>
          Email<br />
          <input type="email" name="email" required />
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>
        <label>
          Property location<br />
          <input type="text" name="location" />
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>
        <label>
          Brief message<br />
          <textarea name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
        </label>
      </p>

      <p>
        <button type="submit">Send enquiry</button>
      </p>
    </form>
  </section>

<footer style="background:#111; color:#fff; margin-top: 2rem;">
  <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem;">
    <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem;">Contact</h2>

    <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">
      Bay of Islands • Kerikeri • Paihia • Opua • Russell (by arrangement)
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">
      Email: <a href="mailto:boiholidayh@gmail.com" style="color:#fff; text-decoration: underline;">boiholidayh@gmail.com</a>
      <br />
      Phone: <a href="tel:+64211394760" style="color:#fff; text-decoration: underline;">+64 21 139 4760</a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 1rem 0 0; opacity: 0.85; font-size: 0.95rem;">
      Reliable local support for absentee holiday home owners. Limited client numbers.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>


</div>


</Layout>
